OL,3,C'It couldn't come soon enough.' Baby
OL,4,Closs certificates offered to more
OL,5,Cparents
OL,7,FRebekah said:"It is real for you from
OL,8,Fthe moment that you find out you are
OL,9,Fhaving a baby. The instant that it's
OL,10,Ftaken away for you, your entire world
OL,11,Fand everything comes crashing down.
OL,13,F"My midwife was actually so lovely.
OL,14,FShe stopped the scan and said: 'I'm so
OL,15,Fsorry, but your baby's heart has
OL,16,Fstopped beating'.
OL,18,F"She just changed my life just in that
OL,19,Fmoment."
