OL,4,Closs certificates offered to more
OL,5,Cparents
OL,7,FAround one in five women in the UK
OL,8,Fexperience the loss of a pregnancy
OL,9,Fbefore 24 weeks. After 24 weeks the
OL,10,Floss is classed as a stillbirth and
OL,11,Fthat has been officially registered
OL,12,Ffor some time.
OL,14,FIn February the law changed allowing
OL,15,Fparents like Rebekah who'd experienced
OL,16,Fbaby loss before 24 weeks to apply for
OL,17,Fa certificate.
OL,19,FBut it only applied to parents who had
OL,20,Fhad a baby before 2018.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
