OL,5,Cparents
OL,7,FToday that has now been extended to
OL,8,Fanyone who's lost a baby before 24
OL,9,Fweeks, however long ago their loss may
OL,10,Fhave been.
OL,12,FRebekah remembers the day her baby
OL,13,Floss certificate arrived through the
OL,14,Fletterbox.
OL,16,F"I didn't realise what it would mean
OL,17,Fto me and holding the certificate and
OL,18,Fseeing Joa's name, that's when it
OL,19,Freally hit me how much I needed this.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
