OL,3,C'It couldn't come soon enough.' Baby
OL,4,Closs certificates offered to more
OL,5,Cparents
OL,7,F"It really helped and I think until
OL,8,Fyou hold that in your hands, you don't
OL,9,Frealise, you don't realise the
OL,10,Fsignificance."
OL,12,FRebekah says having the certificate
OL,13,Fwill also help her to tell her three
OL,14,Fother children about baby Joa as they
OL,15,Fgrow up.
OL,17,FOn today's extension of the law she
OL,18,Fsaid: "There are sometimes women that
OL,19,Fare in their 80's and even older who
OL,20,Fmay never have spoken about their loss
OL,21,Fbecause it just wasn't a thing then.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/11
