OL,3,C'It couldn't come soon enough.' Baby
OL,4,Closs certificates offered to more
OL,5,Cparents
OL,7,F"They've never allowed themselves to
OL,8,Facknowledge that loss and maybe now
OL,9,Fthey can.
OL,11,F"It was a really healing experience to
OL,12,Fhold that certificate in my hands. And
OL,13,FI'm just so glad that there'll be
OL,14,Fwomen now all across England who get
OL,15,Fto do the same thing."
