OL,3,C'It couldn't come soon enough.' Baby
OL,4,Closs certificates offered to more
OL,5,Cparents
OL,7,FZoe and Andy Clark-Coates lost five
OL,8,Fbabies in all. It prompted them to
OL,9,Fstart a charity, the Mariposa Trust,
OL,10,Ffor others in the same boat and
OL,11,Ftoday's announcement comes after years
OL,12,Fof campaigning by them both.
OL,14,FZoe said: "We are absolutely thrilled.
OL,15,FWhen we launched this campaign ten
OL,16,Fyears ago now, it was the hope that it
OL,17,Fwould be available to every bereaved
OL,18,Ffamily.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
