OL,3,C'It couldn't come soon enough.' Baby
OL,4,Closs certificates offered to more
OL,5,Cparents
OL,7,F"And when it came to pass in February,
OL,8,Fobviously there was a time limit. You
OL,9,Fcould only apply if your loss was up
OL,10,Funtil September 2018, and we knew that
OL,11,Fwas temporary.
OL,13,F"But still we were desperate for it to
OL,14,Fbe renewed because we knew millions of
OL,15,Ffamilies were desperate for this
OL,16,Fcertificate.
OL,18,F"So today couldn't come soon enough.
OL,19,FAnd we're absolutely delighted."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/11
