OL,3,C'It couldn't come soon enough.' Baby
OL,4,Closs certificates offered to more
OL,5,Cparents
OL,7,FAndy told us: "The thing about the
OL,8,Fcertificate is for many people, it's
OL,9,Fthe first time they will have had any
OL,10,Fformal recognition. Often it's the
OL,11,Ffirst time their baby's name will ever
OL,12,Fhave been written down on a piece of
OL,13,Fpaper.
OL,15,F"So it's one of those jaw dropping
OL,16,Fmoments to actually be there where you
OL,17,Factually go, I've actually got this
OL,18,Fcertificate. It can go into my family
OL,19,Frecords. My baby existed outside of
OL,20,Fjust my family. The government are
OL,21,Factually recognizing my baby. "
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/11
