OL,3,C'It couldn't come soon enough.' Baby
OL,4,Closs certificates offered to more
OL,5,Cparents
OL,7,F"All of them have said exactly the
OL,8,Fsame thing: 'This is something I
OL,9,Flonged for. I never thought was going
OL,10,Fto happen, and to be able to have it
OL,11,Fwill make so much difference to my
OL,12,Fgrieving journey.'
OL,14,FTo request a baby loss certificate
OL,15,Fvisit www.gov.uk/request-baby-loss-
OL,16,Fcertificate
OL,18,FFor more information, advice and
OL,19,Fsupport about baby loss visit Saying
OL,20,FGoodbye
